    {
      "bookmarkId": "41977958_3_25996-26030",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "25996-26030",
      "markText": "彭德怀在囚窗里翘首盼望毛泽东的答复，就此一等8年，直到他的生命结束。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41977958&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=25996&rangeEnd=26030",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5232dc072808866e52beee?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=25996&rangeEnd=26030"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41977958_3_3364-3433",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3364-3433",
      "markText": "在座的人看出来，毛泽东是在等待彭德怀认错，以便有所表示。　　彭德怀默不作声。他也感觉到，他此时“认错”，就能打开僵局，他的处境会好得多",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41977958&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3364&rangeEnd=3433",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5232dc072808866e52beee?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3364&rangeEnd=3433"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41977958_6_2745-2813",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2745-2813",
      "markText": "面对造反派“你到底跟不跟毛主席走？！”的斥责，陈毅义正辞严地答复说：“我决定跟毛主席走，但是，我不敢保证将来就不反对毛主席的一些意见！”",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41977958&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2745&rangeEnd=2813",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5232dc072808866e52beee?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2745&rangeEnd=2813"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41977958_3_36431-36507",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "36431-36507",
      "markText": "毛泽东阅后批示：“暂时不宜判刑。一切这类专案对犯人都宜调查从严，处理从宽，保护犯人，使他们感到有出路，以便保存活证据，对将来有利，此事不妨请中央一议。”",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41977958&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=36431&rangeEnd=36507",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5232dc072808866e52beee?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=36431&rangeEnd=36507"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41977958_2_1405-1492",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "1405-1492",
      "markText": "林彪重新提起他去年在上海会议上关于“顶峰”的发言，攻击他有野心，是借马克思主义来反对毛主席。康生也攻击朱德“想超过毛主席”、“组织上入党了，思想上还没有入党，还是党外人士。”",
      "totalCount": 130,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41977958&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1405&rangeEnd=1492",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5232dc072808866e52beee?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1405&rangeEnd=1492"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41977958_2_1129-1203",
      "chapterUid": 2,
      "range": "1129-1203",
      "markText": "混进党内、政府内、军队里和各种文化界的资产阶级代表人物，是一批反革命修正主义分子，一旦时机成熟，他们就会要夺取政权，由无产阶级专政变为资产阶级专政。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41977958&chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1129&rangeEnd=1203",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5232dc072808866e52beee?chapterUid=2&rangeStart=1129&rangeEnd=1203"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41977958_3_28254-28302",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "28254-28302",
      "markText": "彭德怀在囚室里给毛泽东写信，给周恩来写信，给中央文革写信，奇怪的是他没有给“副统帅”林彪写过信。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41977958&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=28254&rangeEnd=28302",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e5232dc072808866e52beee?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=28254&rangeEnd=28302"
    },
    {
